#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/understanding_metrics.rst-1
#: ../../content/applications/marketing/marketing_automation/understanding_metrics.rst-1
msgid ""
"What a campaign activity filter tab looks like in Odoo Marketing Automation."
